  "text": "Thank you. I'll ask a couple of questions to clear up the end of the second cycle— the second major cycle. And then we'll go on to the third and last of the major cycles. Can you tell me the life span, the average life span, at the end of the second major cycle? I am Ra. By the end of the second major cycle the life span was as you know it, with certain variations among geographically isolated peoples more in harmony with intelligent energy and less bellicose.",
